::Prowl::

Prowl felt a sharp pain in his arm, though no phisical damage was
being done to him. The pain was from Iron Raptor, though their psychic
bond. He growls and spots Nightstrike, flying at the bot and firing
two missiles, followed by several laser shots.

but she
